Declare a character array of size 50 and read a text that may contain spaces. 
Determine if it is a palindrome (equals its reverse)! For example, "Géza kék az ég" is a palindrome.
Solve the task so that it works for text with spaces as well.
Use the provided code skeleton, and ensure that the return type, function name (identifier), and parameter list of the functions adhere to the given requirements.
